# transcript normalization rules
# Scopes the claude transcript parser and the tool-payload formatters — the
# path every downstream metric is folded from.
#
# Both packages had zero tests before P1; the parser's incremental-read
# contract (ParseFileFromOffset returning a resumable offset with no duplicated
# or lost messages) is what the live monitor depends on, and the formatters
# read the same tool payload keys the metrics file-touch table reads. A silent
# regression here is a silent measurement error everywhere downstream, which is
# why this is scope-graded rather than left to whole-repo test runs.
# Paths are relative to the agentlogs repo root.

pkg/claudelogs/parser.go
pkg/claudelogs/monitor.go
pkg/formatters/formatters.go
pkg/transcript/parser.go
pkg/transcript/unified.go
tests/e2e/scenarios.go
